{"title":"OneUp adds Inline Pump Mount & Bolt-On Tube Strap","link":"https://bikerumor.com/oneup-adds-inline-pump-mount-bolt-on-tube-strap/","date":1695830400000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Inline-Pump-Mount.jpg\" alt=\"oneup inline EDC mini pump cage bolts under the top tube\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Inline-Pump-Mount.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Inline-Pump-Mount-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Inline-Pump-Mount-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Inline-Pump-Mount-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Inline-Pump-Mount-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Inline-Pump-Mount-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Inline-Pump-Mount-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>With more and more bikes adding two-bolt accessory mounts under the top tube, it was only a matter of time before someone (and now, probably, everyone) added dedicated strap mounts for pumps and stuff.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>OneUp Components is first with a mount specifically for their EDC Pump, which is one of my faves. Their high-volume pump is great for MTB (and passably decent for gravel), but its real trick is hiding a complete mini tool and tire plugger kit (or CO2) inside the handle.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/oneup-inline-pump-mount-top-tube-mount.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/oneup-inline-pump-mount-top-tube-mount.jpg\" alt=\"oneup bolt-on tube strap and mini pump cages for bicycles\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/oneup-inline-pump-mount-top-tube-mount.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/oneup-inline-pump-mount-top-tube-mount-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/oneup-inline-pump-mount-top-tube-mount-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/oneup-inline-pump-mount-top-tube-mount-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/oneup-inline-pump-mount-top-tube-mount-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/oneup-inline-pump-mount-top-tube-mount-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/oneup-inline-pump-mount-top-tube-mount-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With the new Inline Pump Mount, you’ll have everything you need for quick repairs and inflation at the ready. The mount is made of durable plastic with a thick rubber strap. The design is easier to clean than a Velcro strap, and won’t slide around, either. It comes with two mounting bolts for $19.50 ($24.50CAD / €19.50 / £24.50).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Top-Tube-Strap-Mount.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Top-Tube-Strap-Mount.jpg\" alt=\"oneup top tube strap holder bolts under the top tube\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Top-Tube-Strap-Mount.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Top-Tube-Strap-Mount-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Top-Tube-Strap-Mount-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Top-Tube-Strap-Mount-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Top-Tube-Strap-Mount-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Top-Tube-Strap-Mount-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Top-Tube-Strap-Mount-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Tube Strap Mount has the same price and the same idea, but with a flatter, wider base for a fold-rolled tube to rest against. Or…</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Tube-Strap-Mount-with-Baguette.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Tube-Strap-Mount-with-Baguette.jpg\" alt=\"oneup top tube strap holder with a baguette in it\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Tube-Strap-Mount-with-Baguette.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Tube-Strap-Mount-with-Baguette-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Tube-Strap-Mount-with-Baguette-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Tube-Strap-Mount-with-Baguette-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Tube-Strap-Mount-with-Baguette-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Tube-Strap-Mount-with-Baguette-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OneUp-Components-Tube-Strap-Mount-with-Baguette-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>…whatever else you want to strap to it. Make a burrito container and I’m sold. Well, actually, I’m already sold. But, burritos.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.oneupcomponents.com\" target=\"_blank\">OneUpComponents.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/oneup-adds-inline-pump-mount-bolt-on-tube-strap/\">OneUp adds Inline Pump Mount &amp; Bolt-On Tube Strap</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"ea82ed8273cca3f921ff071f579e270fa6102ad47a719e946368a5de77d9bcf7","category":"Cycling"}